tr.td:
Ensure: • Set of simulated time series {xsim(1)(t),…,xsim(N)(t)} 1:
for each simulation i=1 to N do 2:
Fourier Transform: X(f)←FFT(x(t)) 3:
Initialize Synthetic Fourier Spectrum: Xsim(f)←0 4:
Preserve and Randomly Scale Daily and Seasonal Components: 5:
for each frequency fp∈{fdaily,fseasonal} do 6:
Ap′←Ap·(1+δ) δ∼U(−α,α) 7:
Xsim(fp)←Ap′·ejϕp 8:
if fp≠0 then 9:
Xsim(−fp)←Ap′·e−jϕp10:
end if11:
end for12:
Randomize Phases of Other Frequencies:13:
for each frequency f∉{fdaily,fseasonal} do14:
ϕrand←U(−π,π)15:
A←|X(f)|16:
Xsim(f)←A·ejϕrand17:
Xsim(−f)←A·e−jϕrand18:
end for19:
Handle DC and Nyquist Components:20:
Xsim(0)←X(0) {DC component remains unchanged}21:
if number of points n is even then22:
Xsim(fNyquist)←X(fNyquist)23:
end if24:
Inverse Fourier Transform: xsim(i)(t)←IFFT(Xsim(f))25:
end for26:
return{xsim(1)(t),…,xsim(N)(t)}
